Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:45.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,mitsumete in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:54.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ai ha tesaguri kurayami no naka de odoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.84,Songs,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be a great night, yeah.
